name: Espolex® WT546
description:
Espolex® WT546 is a thermoplastic elastomer with excellent appearance for microscopic applications, great processing resulting in low cycle times, excellent low temperature ductility, and excellent weldability. It is used for various applications such as airbag covers, airbag chutes, interior trim, and injection molded parts. This product is suitable for Injection molding.

 

Applications:


Airbag Covers
Airbag Chutes
Interior Trim
Handle Grips


 

Features:


Excellent weldability to TPO and PP substrates 
Excellent low temperature ductility 


 

Benefits:


Lower cycle times with easy processing
